It is thrilling to watch our customers discover all the tricks Ember has up its sleeve!
 
The unique perspective from an FPV drone combined with the speed and explosiveness of basketball athletes, juxtaposed with the high frame rate and slow motion capability of the Ember made for an incredibly dynamic shoot.
 
Using the Ember allowed @jaybyrdfilms to see the detail in motion from these amazing athletes at peak performance. 
 
You can’t fight physics so keeping Ember as small and light as possible was top of the list of design requirements! 
 
#freeflyember

Goodbye for now. ✨ That’s a wrap for the 2023 #LasVegasConcours d’Elegance. We’ll see you next year for the 2024 @LasVegasConcours returning November 1-3.

It’s now time to wave the checkered flag at the 2023 @LasVegasConcours as we transition into #UltimateRaceWeek festivities at #WynnLasVegas.

Over 250 classic and exotic cars graced the fairways of #WynnGolfClub this weekend, celebrated by collectors and auto admirers from around the world. From the Exhibition to the Tour d’Elegance parade on Las Vegas Boulevard, these days will be remembered, talked about and dreamt of for a long time to come. 

We look forward to welcoming you next year as #LasVegasConcours returns November 1–3. 

For more information regarding #UltimateRaceWeek, including all F1 experiences, please visit WynnLasVegas.com.

Sunday is here and it’s time to wave the checkered flag on the #UltimateRaceWeek here at #WynnLasVegas. 🏁 A celebration we will all remember forever —pop ups, premieres, cars, guest stars, friends, fans and many more — all culminating in a magical fireworks display and lots of Champagne. 🏆
